    "description": "<br><br>《极度之刃》是一款快节奏，基于物理的动作游戏。利用动能惯性，飞檐走壁，砍杀敌人。同时利用控制“子弹时间”和挥刀反弹子弹来体验一场即兴并充满无限可能的战斗！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/2558d7f2e5af65496de9d201484b289d.poster.avif?t=1764776248\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/2558d7f2e5af65496de9d201484b289d.webm?t=1764776248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/2558d7f2e5af65496de9d201484b289d.mp4?t=1764776248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在充满了挑战的未知房间中冲刺，砍杀，反射<br></li><li> 操控“子弹时间”，展现自己的霸道风范<br></li><li> 逐步解开你的身世之谜</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ffc7b64abdd8a4e9ede8cc2bc6b872c5.poster.avif?t=1764776248\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ffc7b64abdd8a4e9ede8cc2bc6b872c5.webm?t=1764776248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/ffc7b64abdd8a4e9ede8cc2bc6b872c5.mp4?t=1764776248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即将推出的新特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 更多风格多样，富有挑战性的关卡<br></li><li> 更多新的游戏玩法要素<br></li><li> 更多新的环境设计<br></li><li> 以及更多需要你探索的背景故事</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834740/extras/f2f8effd2c51fa11cbe31f3082b3b614.poster.avif?t=1764776248\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/183